title: 820-00165-A Orange light and no fan spinning.
message:
Hi,
This unit was Liquid damaged, turn on and works but fan spin very fast so i did ultraso for 10 minutes 
and now it has stable orange light but no fan spinning. and i see liquid was arouns U7100.

PPBUS_G3H =8.57v
PPDCIN_G3H_ISOL =16.84v

PP5V_S5= 5v

PP3V3_S5 =3.33
PM_BATLOW_L =3.33v

Any help please

title: 820-00165-A Orange light and no fan spinning.
message:
Something got damaged in the UC.
Check for knocked off components, broken trace...

Trigger SMC_ONOFF_L and see if PM_PWRBTN_L reacts.
If yes, check also PM_SLP_Sx_L signals for any reaction; like a simply pulse at least.

Try to start in SMC bypass mode.
